16 (a) Except as provided in this section, this division does not apply to charter
17 counties.
18 (b) The following provisions of this division apply to a charter county:
19 (19) § 4–217 (PATUXENT RESEARCH REFUGE);
20 [(19)] (20) Title 4, Subtitle 5 (Accessory Dwelling Units);
